commit message: Linked to Google Play from README
Added link to F-Droid in README.

Support for adding account manually

This patch is adding the possibility to add account manually without the
need to scan the QR code. It requires to fill in the name of the account
the secret key and choose one of the authentication type (TOTP, HOTP).

Updated icons for multiple screen resolutions

This patch is adding icons for multiple screen resolution which assures
that the icons will have no blurred edges. The icons were taken from
Android platform v22 (platforms/android-22/data/res/).

Merge pull request #15 from jtyr/icons

Updated icons for multiple screen resolutions

Support for Issuer in the list of codes

This patch is adding the support for Issuer in the list of codes. It's
automatically extracted from the account name if it's in the
issuer:label format.

Merge pull request #16 from jtyr/issuer

Support for Issuer in the list of codes
